descriptionTranslated: We are looking for new roommates for our student house in the Nieuwe Kijk in 't Jatstraat. The house is located in the centre of the city, just outside of the inner city center, and within a 5 minutes walk from the Grote Markt. The room that will be available as per August 1st  is 14  m2. There are curtains  before the windows and laminaat on the floor.  The room is on the first floor of the appartment, next to the kitchen and the small  dining annex tv room (GK).  The room has its own balcony from 6m long and 1m wide, with a view on the Noorderhaven.   The kitchen, bathroom annex washing room, and the toilet are also shared with the other 4 students living in the house. There is a huge roof terrace  next to the GK that belongs to another house, but which can be used under strict conditions, to be communicated when room is rented.    If you are interested you can send me an email for an appointment to see the house and the room.
